snippet.title: Umineko no Naku Koro ni Chiru PS3 OP - Inanna no Mita Yume
snippet.description:
Opening movie of Umineko no Naku Koro ni Chiru ~Nocturne of Truth and Illusions~ (PS3). Song title: "Inanna no Mita Yume" (Inanna's Dream). This OP also plays in the PC version if you have the UmiTweak patch applied when you start up the game, before reaching the main menu.

MP3: http://www.mediafire.com/download/9kfohltj39aadr6/Umineko_no_Naku_Koro_ni_Chiru_PS3_OP.mp3

UmiTweak: http://uminekofix.wikia.com/wiki/Tweaking_Umineko_Wiki
